  "storyline": "Konthayum Poonulum is a Malayalam Family drama directed by Jijo Antony. A baker rushes home to be with his heavily pregnant wife. A police officer, picks up a lady from the streets, but she disappears into thin air, making him believe that she isn't of the human kind. A story which gives prominence to friendship, family and focuses on certain social issues related to religion.",
